---
title: Peach & Nectarine Orzo Salad with Feta, Cucumber, and Mint
description: A few minutes under the broiler allows juicy peaches and nectarines to develop even more sweetness. Refreshing cucumber, mint, and lemon keep this salad feeling fresh and light, while orzo provides a hearty base.
